                  <ab type="description">Three persons (a man and two women) are standing next to a machine and are talking and smiling. It seems that they observe the machine, which is some sort of a press for textile. The man and woman in the front are dressed in white. In the far background, we can see the head of a worker, some work materials, as well as the ceiling and the neon lights.</ab>
